node.title: Matchpoint: Aussie Open champ Djokovic has visa cancelled over anti-vax stance
node.description: The tennis world No.1 insists he will protest the Australian Government decision.
node.content: ["Australian Open champion Novak Djokovic pledge to fight his latest setback to a title defence at Melbourne this month.", "Detained several hours at Tullamarine Airport over a documentation blunder, the Serbian world tennis No.1 has reportedly had his visa cancelled over his repeated refusal to undergo COVID-19 vaccination.", "More to come"]
